social_posts.post_text: Damn shout out AI got me looking like B list actor on Star Trek 🤝

FALL IN LOVE IS OUT - Jawny thank you for bringing me into your world. You have no idea what it’s done for my soul as a producer, I listen to this song in particular and feel an immense sense of pride. The world is lucky to have you! The whole album process was a dream but the week we made this in El Paso with Elie is truly something I’ll never forget. Elie you’re a wizard, this song reached heights I didn’t even think were possible until we all sat in that live room and performed it. Album on the wayyy ❤️
Cupids got me in a choke hold 💘

JAWNY! Man what a ride even going thru the pictures for this dump got me mad emotional. Today is the big day, the debut album from the legend @jawnyutah is out now and was blessed enough to be trusted to executive produce with J. Got so many people to thank for the magical experience that was making this album, big love to all of our collaborators @eliethebear @captaincuts @songsaboutdreams @slimdan9 @solomonophonic @marinelli @jamiesierota @ilanrubin 🤘🏼🔥 I could get substantial sappier here but all I’m gonna say is listen to this album top to bottom, we sequenced every moment of it and made the album of our dreams. Enjoy ❤️

CAFUNÉ! The lovely and talented @wearecafune tapped me in to jam with them and I am soooo happy they did. I’ve known these guys for a good 6 years now and it was a beautiful time to be able to work on their new song Perspective with them. YAHM IT 🔥

GAYLE! @gayle You are the real deal, amazing vision and so insanely talented. Felt like this song just came right out of us and @carliehanson that day. Thanks for being fearless in your craft and for letting me in your world! EVERYBODY HATES ME OUT NOW 🔥

They don’t see the vision
DEMISE! @wearecafune I have so much love for you guys thanks for letting me be an unofficial third member in the stu. Making music with y’all is the best 🫶Go jam Denise nowwwww 😈
International rockstar @jawnyutah back like he never left. Always a joy creating with you J. Made this bad boy with Canadian prime minister @princedcf 🙌🏼 jam our song Boy Scout out now

We’ve got ourselves a double header this week 🎶

Invisible Man is out now on Oliver’s new album Alone in a Crowd 💙 Big love to my brothers at @olivertree and @caseymattson_ felt good to have the Alien Boys back in the lab.

Jerm! Aka @jeremyzucker just dropped his beautiful new song This Time. Thank you for letting me play a small part in this one and trusting me to help you get it over the finish line! 🫶
Got one of these fun Spotify Playlists. Thanks to my squad @overall.mgmt and @hipgnosisstudios for making it happen 🫶 catalog isn’t fully updated yet but check the link if you’re curious 🏆

Bad Blood with @boywithuke is out now! Big thanks to my amazing collaborators @yamurai_egg @antonrundberg @juliackarlsson for such a fun day so happy it’s out 💙

Also! @official_g_i_dle have dropped their EP HEAT. Our song I DO is the lead single and has been on top 40 radio doing its things💪🏼 shoutout the A Team @rogetchahayed @blaiserailey and @drewlove 💙
Any homies on the voting committee drop your boy a little vote ❤️

Got two wonderful releases today!

Made Midnight Oil with my brother @whethan @elleyduhe @hamdimusic and @iamzikai! The vibes were immaculate that day thank you guys for such a great time. 🕯️

Also my incredible friends in @wearecafune have dropped their EP Love Songs for the End today! The last song from our batch Shadowboxing is out now along side Perspective and Demise 🖤💙 Congrats guys.

Congrats to @bludnymph on her debut album! Our song ORAL HEX is on there and it rips 🫡 Kya goes without saying that you bodied it and @solly.not.solly @jfinkelz @cirkut you guys are 🐐🐐🐐 was such a great time making this.

This is a big full circle moment for me. I got my chops up as a producer with my best friend Isaac flipping your songs @mayerhawthorne so to be on one of your albums is something I’m incredibly proud of! Jam our song Physical Touch, made by Mayer, myself, @cody.dear @jesseboykins3rd and @rodaidh mixed by the one and only @jeffellisworldwide 🔥🔥 thanks for having me man you’re sounding as good as ever 🤝
And we’re only getting started 😈
